| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0569 — Recovery Inhibition (spacebears)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a6a82710-f76a-5fcc-92ef-0f6d6169a7fc"
